{"tid":561570,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"這就是骨氣！華碩拒絕資料轉移，關閉支那機房！","createTime":"2018-02-15T06:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T16:00:12.000Z","uid":48234,"like":371,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"651d1a2fa687c1563d677355dd5485409cd65363","tid":561570,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:28:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.android-hk.com/news/asus-close-china-server-android-hk-13218/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.android-hk.com%2Fnews%2Fasus-close-china-server-android-hk-13218%2F&d=%2Ff3dVIMZAgN3cVdO%2BLpXNACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=630d674f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.android-hk.com/news/asus-close-china-server-android-hk-13218/</a><br />\n為了進一步控制用戶的數據資料，早前支那立例要求各公司的雲端服務必須要轉移至支那地區資料庫，配合有關部門的審查。對於要進入支那市場的品牌如蘋果等，當然搶先配合有關部門的任何要求，並已經將「iCloud」營運權交予「雲上貴州」公司。<br />\n<br />\n不過對於各大品牌來說，是不是只有「配合政策」這一條路呢？台灣品牌華碩就給了我們另一個答案。華碩宣佈，為了「配合」支那政府的政策，公司將會在 5月1日起直接關閉於上海的機房服務，現有用戶如果仍想使用華碩的雲端服務的話，需要到專用網站重新登錄，並連接至其他地區的機房繼續使用。簡單來說就是要連接到海外的伺服器才能繼續使用有關的雲端服務。<br />\n<br />\n對比蘋果，大家又怎看華碩的做法呢？果然比蘋果更具風骨吧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8a8a8674c03d5e87990c4d09291073e33739bb","tid":561570,"uid":37232,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"放心底板9成用asrock / asus"},{"pid":"c15e0550351dd69473fc2303e6d44b12b96e3715","tid":561570,"uid":48234,"like":130,"dislike":1,"score":129,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T07:24:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">ASUS嘅風骨勝過一萬個打手</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915cf83b7a04f5edc5abbf65af9b04ef8516f7e8","tid":561570,"uid":88374,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"